g/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ef6abb0a7ce10503367242c433366691dcfafba","tid":2363033,"uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:37:10.000Z","msg":"【更新】<br />\n<br />\n英國本月底開始接受港人申請BNO留英簽證，有建制派議員提出應禁止港人擁有雙重國籍。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，國籍問題屬敏感，回歸前的討論亦令很多市民關心，礙於歷史原因，中英兩國政府對如何處理英國國民(海外)護照有共識，如有人單方面偏離共識，另一方要採取一些行動是理所當然，但到目前為止，她不知有何具體方案正在討論，特區政府亦沒有提出如何處理有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席行政會議前表示，有關說法是由一名行政會議成員提出，但行政會議並無討論有關問題。<br />\n<br />\n她又說，當國家及特區受外國不合理制裁，無理由甚麼也不做，特區政府會配合中央政府採取需要的反制措施。"},{"pid":"0bf417540ae334c2d435832179430699cda6a26a","tid":2363033,"uid":23061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8aabf8d95e84454eee7eb5a1ace7cdb79c211c27","tid":2363033,"uid":24660,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:12:43.000Z","msg":"Never believe in anything until it has been officially denied."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"堅"},{"pid":"a3805651b17ba83666b825e6e010884418145def","tid":2363033,"uid":265318,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:46:14.000Z","msg":"國藉問題輪到市長你討論？<br />\n痾篤尿照下自己先"},{"pid":"a46ecd56f811a7ba421cd97e92bd96aa02b40cd4","tid":2363033,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:48:47.000Z","msg":"支持取消所有BNO中國國籍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f835cff476399e343dfdc1c287bc5b15a6ce7f98","tid":2363033,"uid":308041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T02:59:31.000Z","msg":"佢自己都想去英國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629a5d4c905f87c82da7cf68e4047e71dfba092f","tid":2363033,"uid":8662,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6ef6abb0a7ce10503367242c433366691dcfafba","tid":2363033,"u